0. Make sure VERSION has no u suffix

1. Generate manual html for the program

1.5 Update the translations

2. Run make to compile/check, then make dist to build

3. Verify installation works with an empty MySQL database

4. Commit any changes made as the release

5. Copy all sheltermanager* files to rawsoaa8:/var/www/deb

6. Update news page on site

7. Update changelog3.txt on site

8. Update version on site

9. Update deb package on rawsoaa8

10. Update Launchpad release

11. Update ASM online with "make smcomstable"

12. Update twitter and facebook

13. Update manual with lulu

14. tag and commit again

15. DON'T DO THIS - BZR TAKES FOREVER AND IT OFFER NO BENEFIT
    Make a new branch for this release:
    cd .. && cp sheltermanager sheltermanager_VERSION
    cd sheltermanager_VERSION
    bzr push --remember lp:~bobintetley/sheltermanager/VERSION
    bzr pull --remember lp:~bobintetley/sheltermanager/VERSION
    bzr info

16. Mark the new branch as mature in the launchpad UI.

17. Return to trunk working folder, update dev env version number

